<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Upload Image</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
		<h2>Upload Vehicle's license plate image</h2>
		<p>Upload vehicle's license plate image to generate traffic ticket and send it via mail.</p>
		<form id="uploadForm" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post">
			<input type="file" name="userFile" />
			<input type="submit" value="Upload File" name="submit">
		</form>
		<br>
		<br>
		<p>Download any image from Graphathon album at <a target="_blank" href="https://neerajnegi174.imgur.com">https://neerajnegi174.imgur.com</a> and then upload.</p>
		<p>Currently database has entries for these images only.</p>
		<br>
		<br>
		<br>
		<p>If Heroku app is not working then please run it locally by following below steps:</p>
		<p>Prerequisites:</p>
		<p>--Node Js installed</p>
		<ol>
			<li>Download zipped file from <a target ="_blank" href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/mqda1rbht7k2qa7/online_traffic_ticket_generator.zip?dl=0">dropbox</a></li>
			<li>Extract file and go to online_traffic_ticket_generator folder.</li>
			<li>Run npm install command and then run node index.js to run app locally.</li>
		</ol>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
